.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-DATASOURCE-DIFF 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.8.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-datasource\-diff \- Compare datasource inventory from a local bundle against live Grafana and print an operator\-summary diff report.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util datasource diff [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Compare datasource inventory from a local bundle against live Grafana and print an operator\-summary diff report.
.PP
Use this when you want a concise live\-versus\-local difference report before import.
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-diff\-dir
local datasource bundle to compare.
.TP
.B \-\-input\-format
choose inventory or provisioning.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Compare datasource inventory from a local bundle against live Grafana and print an operator\-summary diff report.
.EX
grafana-util datasource diff --url http://localhost:3000 --basic-user admin --basic-password admin --diff-dir ./datasources --input-format inventory
.EE
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBgrafana-util\fR(1),
\fBgrafana-util-datasource\fR(1)
